title: Spycatcher - Peter Wright
description:
I had such a good response to The Iron Curtain, I thought I would upload the book Spycatcher - I found it in some e-library.

This book was notorious when it came out for blowing the lid on the security establishment, exposing its embarrassing secrets and so forth. It was banned in Britain - for all I know, it may still be.

Pirates should enjoy this kind of mayhem.
